36:20.220 --> 36:21.763
- So, Mike?

36:21.763 --> 36:23.556
Your blade held up really well.

36:23.556 --> 36:25.475
You can see,
right here,

36:25.475 --> 36:28.061
where that bullet
went right across the blade.

36:28.061 --> 36:29.938
