36:29.938 --> 36:31.773
Welcome to the club!

36:31.773 --> 36:33.024
- [chuckles]
[sighs]

36:35.026 --> 36:38.071
- Bladesmiths,
this is the kill test.

36:38.071 --> 36:40.156
Let's see how deadly
your weapons are.

36:40.156 --> 36:41.366
Jon, you're up first.
You ready?

36:41.366 --> 36:42.909
- Rock and roll.

36:42.909 --> 36:44.619
I built this thing to kill.

36:44.619 --> 36:46.871
It's not some flashy
museum piece.

36:46.871 --> 36:49.916
<i>♪ ♪</i>

