38:21.132 --> 38:23.009
it will kill.

38:23.009 --> 38:25.637
Good job.
- Thank you.

38:25.637 --> 38:27.764
- Gentlemen,
your blades are strong.

38:27.764 --> 38:29.933
Your blades will kill.

