But a military weapon
has to take the fight

38:31.976 --> 38:34.020
to our enemies,
anywhere in the world.

38:34.020 --> 38:36.564
A sharp blade
should cut effortlessly

38:36.564 --> 38:38.272
through these lush vines.

38:40.527 --> 38:41.903
- Jon, you're up first.
You ready?

38:41.903 --> 38:44.739
- Let's rock.
- Let's do this.

38:44.739 --> 38:46.533
- It's all down to this,
this is the moment

38:46.533 --> 38:49.160
