39:27.615 --> 39:28.908
- Let's do this.

39:31.202 --> 39:34.455
<i>[intense music]</i>

39:34.455 --> 39:41.379
<i>♪ ♪</i>

39:43.089 --> 39:46.718
<i>♪ ♪</i>

39:46.718 --> 39:47.927
All right, Mike,
let's talk about

39:47.927 --> 39:49.387
your cutlass, right here.

39:49.387 --> 39:51.222
The curved edge you have here
